Use the Shazam Core API to define the song by uploading the file. Get detailed data on songs and artists. Site: www.shazam.com Support: tipsters@rapi.one / t.me/api_tipsters

Use the Shazam Core API to define the song by uploading the file. Get detailed data on songs and artists. Ready-made lists of charts in cities and countries. Covers, video clips, and lyrics.

Shazam identifies a song by creating a unique digital fingerprint to match what youre hearing with one of the millions of songs in the Shazam database.
